getInviteHoldingAddress(uint256).details: Getter to discover the $X holding address of a particular NFT

lockURI().details: Changes the uri admin to an empty address, preventing further changes to the URI

mintInviteNFT().details: Mints an NFT that represents .01 $X and exactly one invite. Easy to list on OpenSea

tokenURI(uint256).details: A custom URI that will hopefully point towards generative artwork in the future?

updateDevFee(uint256).details: Changes fee for minting or using an invite NFT.

updateDevFeeCollector(address).details: Changes the address that recieves the dev fees

updateURIAdmin(address).details: Changes the address responsible for managing the URI base

updateURIBase(string).details: Changes the URI base. EX: moving visual assets to a new server and maybe new domain

useAndGenerateInviteNFT(uint256).details: Destroys NFT, sends .01 $X to msg.sender, moves .01 into a new invite holding address, issues msg.sender a new NFT representing one $X invite
